    public abstract class SprocketsListFragment
extends ListFragment
implements ActionModePresenter
    Injects content Views, saves the instance state of Icicle fields and restores them when recreated, hides and restores the list's ActionMode as requested (e.g. in a NavigationDrawerActivity).
